Create a new rails app called pin_board that uses postgres db and skips installing test::unit. 
	In console: 
	rails new pin_board -d postgresql --skip-test-unit
	rake db:create 
	rake db:migrate

Make sure file works in browswer: 
	cd pin_board
	rails s
	In browswer: 
	localhost:3000
	Should see rails message. 

Check Versions etc: 
	ruby -v
	rails -v
	rvm info
	gemset
	etc

